<http://dx.doi.org/10.1649/072.065.0301>
    bibo:endPage "212" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "The Coleopterists Bulletin" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2011-09-30" ;
    bibo:startPage "197" ;
    bibo:volume "65" ;
    dc:creator "Barr, Cheryl B." ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "BryelmisBarr (Coleoptera: Elmidae: Elminae), a New Genus of Riffle Beetle with Three New Species from the Pacific Northwest, U. S. A." ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340577>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340579>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340573>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340571>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340575> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340577>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Known distribution of Bryelmis spp. in North America: B. idahoensis (circles), B. rivularis (squares), and B. siskiyou (triangles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5340577/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340579>
    dc:description "Figs. 11–13. 11) Fern Creek, Clearwater Co., ID, type locality of Bryelmis idahoensis; 12) Dragsaw Spring, Humboldt Co., CA, habitat of Bryelmis siskiyou; 13) Hell Roaring Creek, Jefferson Co., WA, type locality of Bryelmis rivularis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5340579/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340573>
    dc:description "Figs. 5–7. Male genitalia of Bryelmis spp. 5) B. idahoensis, dorsal view; 6) B. siskiyou, dorsal view; 7) B. rivularis, a) Dorsal view, b) Lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5340573/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340571>
    dc:description "Figs. 3–4. Habitus of Bryelmis idahoensis. a) Dorsal, b) Lateral. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5340571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5340575>
    dc:description "Figs. 8–9. Habitus of Bryelmis spp. 8) B. rivularis, a) Dorsal, b) Lateral; 9) B. siskiyou, a) Dorsal, b) Lateral. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5340575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

